4.3.2 cmd_rsync
---------------

The cmd_rsync parameter must not be commented out, and it must point to
a working version of `rsync'. If it doesn't, the program just will not
work at all.

   Please note that if you are using IRIX, there is another program
named `rsync' that is different than the real `rsync' most people know
of. If you're on an IRIX machine, you should double check this.


